graphs.text: #   This is the innermost recto panel of a six-panel fold-out.
#   continues recipe pages. 3 recipes, 3 text paras
# There are 5 labels alternating with 4 plants.
# plant [1,2] - light coloured root, dark leaves, stem
# plant [1,3] - three roots, hairy base of stem, dark flowers
# plant [1,4] - large twotone root, light leaf
# The {blot} looks like part of a plant rather than a flaw
# There are 4 labels alternating with 3 plants
# plant [2,1] - large striped root, dark leaf
# plant [2,3] - large striped root - mostly dark
# There are four labels alternating with 3 plants.
# plant [3,1] - light coloured roots, dark leaves
# plant [3,2] - light coloured roots with heads, dark flower
# plant [3,3] - light coloured roots, dark flower (berries?)
